Section I:
- Import the project (src folder) in an IDE (such as Eclipse or IntelliJ)
- Copy the "Project3Dataset-A" and "Project3Dataset-B" directory (dataset) in the working directory
- Setup SDK (JRE: JavaSE-1.8)
- Run the main method in the Main.java file

The program will not terminate unless an invalid command is given or it is stopped.

Section II:
Tests:
SELECT A.Col1, A.Col2, B.Col1, B.Col2 FROM A, B WHERE A.RandomV = B.RandomV
SELECT count(*) FROM A, B WHERE A.RandomV > B.RandomV
SELECT Col2, SUM(RandomV) FROM A GROUP BY Col2
SELECT Col2, SUM(RandomV) FROM B GROUP BY Col2
SELECT Col2, AVG(RandomV) FROM A GROUP BY Col2
SELECT Col2, AVG(RandomV) FROM B GROUP BY Col2

